room_title: Escape room "Detention" by Armadillo Escape Room Adventures in Houston
room_address: 417 Gentry St. Units E&F Old Town Spring, TX 77373
room_description: Summer is sadly over but you're not ready to let it go even though it is the first week of school. You were trying to start the school year off right... but... you got caught breaking the rules! Sent straight to detention after school. Will you be able to collect the items you need for the beach and pull an epic prank to get out of detention early so you can enjoy one last day of summer with your friends?
